The paper presents an index structure for efficient SimRank computation, which involves graph similarity measures. This topic is closely related to several computer science sub-categories, including data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), social and information networks (cs.SI), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
